</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3776556ED7C3818FC9AF8BAFBDAF835" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BD236DDED7C3818FC9AF8BAFBDAF835" blockId="557.[810,1452,955,2070]" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FC9AF8BAFC25F84F" bold="true" box="[863,992,1908,1934]" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">Etymology</emphasis>
. The generic name is from the Greek 
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FCEFF858FC9AF871" box="[810,863,1942,1968]" italics="true" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">scoli</emphasis>
(=curved, crooked) and 
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FB55F858FB0EF86E" box="[1168,1227,1942,1967]" italics="true" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">soma</emphasis>
(=body), referring the curved body of the adult female in species of the new genus. Gender neuter.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3776556ED7C381AFC9AF832FE21F903" lastPageId="559" lastPageNumber="560" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD236DDED7C381AFC9AF832FE21F903" blockId="557.[810,1452,955,2070]" lastBlockId="559.[136,778,1159,1730]" lastPageId="559" lastPageNumber="560" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FC9AF832FC09F7D7" bold="true" box="[863,972,2044,2070]" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7C3818FC10F832FB93F7D7" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[981,1110,2044,2070]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Scoliosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen.nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FC10F832FB93F7D7" box="[981,1110,2044,2070]" italics="true" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">Scoliosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7C3818FB9CF832FB7AF7D7" box="[1113,1215,2044,2070]" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FB9CF832FB7DF7D7" bold="true" box="[1113,1208,2044,2070]" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">gen.nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
resembles 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7C3818FAF1F832FA69F7D7" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[1332,1452,2044,2070]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Gallincola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7C3818FAF1F832FA69F7D7" box="[1332,1452,2044,2070]" italics="true" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">Gallincola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFF4DFB49FF30FB63" box="[136,245,1159,1186]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFF4DFB49FF2BFB60" bold="true" box="[136,238,1159,1185]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
: they have a similar body form and both have a strong distal tooth on the mandibular gnathobase. Interestingly, both live in galls in solitary ascidians. However, the cephalic appendages of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFD8EFB23FD09FAC6" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[587,716,1261,1287]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Scoliosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD8EFB23FD09FAC6" box="[587,716,1261,1287]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Scoliosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFD1CFB23FF7EFAEB" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD1CFB23FF71FAE8" bold="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
are much more simplified than in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFD93FAC1FD0BFAE8" authority="The" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[598,718,1295,1321]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Gallincola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD93FAC1FD0BFAE8" box="[598,718,1295,1321]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Gallincola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFD1CFAC1FF7EFA8D" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD1CFAC1FF71FA8A" bold="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
The mandibular exopod is armed with 5 setae in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFF4DFA9DFEC5FAAC" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[136,256,1363,1389]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Gallincola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFF4DFA9DFEC5FAAC" box="[136,256,1363,1389]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Gallincola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFEC2FA9DFEB7FAAF" box="[263,370,1363,1390]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFEC2FA9DFEA9FAAC" bold="true" box="[263,364,1363,1389]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
but with 4 setae in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFD95FA9DFD14FAAC" authority="The" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[592,721,1363,1389]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Scoliosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD95FA9DFD14FAAC" box="[592,721,1363,1389]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Scoliosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFD1CFA9DFF7EFA51" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFD1CFA9DFF71FA51" bold="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
The maxillule of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFEBAFABBFE32FA4E" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[383,503,1397,1423]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Gallincola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFEBAFABBFE32FA4E" box="[383,503,1397,1423]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Gallincola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFE38FAB8FDA2FA51" box="[509,615,1398,1424]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFE38FAB8FDA5FA51" bold="true" box="[509,608,1398,1424]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
bears as many as 9 setae on the arthrite and has a biramous palp but this appendage in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFEE2FA77FE6DFA12" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[295,424,1465,1491]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Scoliosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFEE2FA77FE6DFA12" box="[295,424,1465,1491]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Scoliosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFE75FA74FDD9FA15" box="[432,540,1466,1492]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFE75FA74FDD3FA15" bold="true" box="[432,534,1466,1492]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">gen. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
bears a total of only 5 setae on the arthrite and has a rudimentary, lobate palp. Othernotable differences include: in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EED7E381AFDD9FA33FD58F9D6" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[540,669,1533,1559]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Scoliosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED7E381AFDD9FA33FD58F9D6" box="[540,669,1533,1559]" italics="true" pageId="559" pageNumber="560">Scoliosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED7E381AFD67FA30FCCFF9D9" box="[674,778,1534,1560]" pageId="559" pageNumber="560" rank="genus">
